            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As it is your intention to take the two Amendments you have selected together, will you permit, if necessary, a Division to be taken on each Amendment?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7bf04688-9943-4043-8023-78b170c77685" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
