            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0da5a7f0-8e3e-4ece-b432-b858a5c4a506" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-19/debates/7b2e22b6-4317-4c1a-92b3-3383fb022cd8/FifthSchedule%E2%80%94(PurchaseTax(AmendmentsOfScheduleOfChargeableGoods))#contribution-0da5a7f0-8e3e-4ece-b432-b858a5c4a506">
