<p class="">I gathered from the hon. Gentleman's opening remarks that he was dealing with his Amendment, which has not been selected.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-04babcea-d260-428d-8085-82b95c88d0fb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
