            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-0f4e560a-d4dd-43e0-bfc9-3157c0ce0cc9">
                The Deputy-Chairman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0f4e560a-d4dd-43e0-bfc9-3157c0ce0cc9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
